OL,3,CGang who posed as electricity workers
OL,4,Cto power cannabis farms jailed
OL,6,FWorkers from Elev8 Civils and
OL,7,FUtilities Limited drove company-
OL,8,Fbranded vans to locations where they
OL,9,Fwould cordon off areas, dig up
OL,10,Fpavements and splice into cables to
OL,11,Fprovide direct feeds into cannabis
OL,12,Ffarms, Liverpool Crown Court heard.
OL,14,FOn Friday, seven men were jailed, and
OL,15,Fone handed a suspended sentence, for
OL,16,Ftheir roles in the enterprise, ` which
OL,17,Finvestigators found was involved in
OL,18,Fsetting up factories in 32 different
OL,19,Fpolice force areas between November
OL,20,F2020 and February 2024.
