OL,3,CGang who posed as electricity workers
OL,4,Cto power cannabis farms jailed
OL,6,FThe group, headed by company directors
OL,7,FRoss McGinn, 33, from Huyton,
OL,8,FMerseyside, and Andrew Roberts, 42,
OL,9,Ffrom Wigan, offered their services to
OL,10,FAlbanian organised crime groups,
OL,11,Finvestigators from the North West
OL,12,FRegional Organised Crime Unit said.
OL,14,FThe firm was registered on Companies
OL,15,FHouse and both McGinn and Roberts had
OL,16,FLinkedIn profiles in which they posted
OL,17,Fphotos of apparently legitimate work
OL,18,Fto promote the company.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
