OL,3,CGang who posed as electricity workers
OL,4,Cto power cannabis farms jailed
OL,6,FThrough Operation Spark, set up to
OL,7,Finvestigate the company, police seized
OL,8,Fcannabis plants with a street value of
OL,9,Fup to #21 million from more than 100
OL,10,Ffarms, most of which were occupied by
OL,11,FAlbanian nationals, acting as
OL,12,Fgardeners, who said they had been
OL,13,Ftrafficked to the UK.
OL,15,FFootage recovered by investigators
OL,16,Fshowed electrical explosions as the
OL,17,Fgang dug into lines on a street in
OL,18,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
