OL,3,CGang who posed as electricity workers
OL,4,Cto power cannabis farms jailed
OL,6,FA photo found on a phone showed
OL,7,FRoberts with burns to his face thought
OL,8,Fto have been suffered while work was
OL,9,Fcarried out.
OL,11,FSentencing, Judge David Potter said
OL,12,Fall the defendants were "driven by
OL,13,Fgreed to continue this illegal trade".
OL,15,FTheir work was "pivotal" in setting up
OL,16,Fcannabis farms discovered in premises
OL,17,Fincluding a former hotel, shops, a
OL,18,Fnightclub, a pub and an empty
OL,19,Fdepartment store, he said.
