OL,3,CGang who posed as electricity workers
OL,4,Cto power cannabis farms jailed
OL,6,FHe added: "They did so often in broad
OL,7,Fdaylight and in plain sight. They used
OL,8,Fthe cover of liveried vehicles,
OL,9,Fsignage, barriers and high visibility
OL,10,Fclothing to appear as though they were
OL,11,Fcarrying out legitimate street works."
OL,13,FMcGinn, on videolink from prison,
OL,14,Fwiped away tears as he was jailed for
OL,15,Ffive years four months.
OL,17,FRoberts was sentenced to six years.
OL,19,Ffive others were given sentences
OL,20,Franging from two and a half years to
OL,21,Ffive years and three months.
